"sable" is a tool for creating HTML documents from Python source code.

It is a simple, single-file package that can be downloaded from PyPI and installed with pip.

The package contains the following files:

sable.py

sable.py is the main file. It contains the main class Sable and the following functions:

__init__

__init__ is the constructor for Sable. It takes the following arguments:

title: the
